<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="331" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="16.[835,1474,385,440]" pageId="16" pageNumber="331">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[835,979,385,409]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="331">Etymology. –</emphasis>
“Lek” means small in Thai and it refers to the small size of the species
